[I] ASN.1 to C Compiler

[T] Asn1c is a free, open source compiler of ASN.1 specifications into C source code.
[T] It supports a range of ASN.1 syntaxes, including ISO/IEC/ITU ASN.1 1988, '94,
[T] '97, 2002 and later amendments.

[U] https://lionet.info/asn1c/

[A] Lev Walkin <vlm@lionet.info>
